name: The One With Too Much Info
description:
A picture is worth a thousand words. But without the context of the description, how many words is it then? Check out the logo in the dashboard. Usually you can see a description on the image but it doesn't seem to render. Maybe you can go beyond Kibana and inspect the code to find the hidden info!
